body_html:
quantized mobilenet is created by carefully modifying the training graph. The TensorFlow team is preparing a document with details, including software support for training other model similarly.

Unfortunately, there's no way to use quantized inception at the moment. We are working on supporting 'quantized_weights' as soon as possible.
